data.description: An entertainer's delight! This lovely 4 bed, 3 bath home offers so much versatility! Step inside to a large great room and dining area with an open-concept kitchen that offers white cabinetry, granite countertops and backsplash, a pantry, and an island. This tri-split wing floor plan offers so much flexibility and privacy. The den, located at the front is very well sized and features a closet with shelving and could be used as an office or easily converted to a 5th bedroom.  The gorgeous hard surface flooring throughout makes this home stylish and easy to maintain. Step outside and you'll find a nice-sized inground pool and an awesome outdoor kitchen that spans the length of the covered patio, you'll also discover a lovely pergola and an area for those who like basketball. Be sure to check out the tons of producing fruit trees. Don't forget this home offers a 3 car garage with overhead storage. This amazing home is an entertainer's delight inside and out and is ready for you!
